  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates the therapeutic potential of bone marrow mesenchymal stem cell transplantation for spinal cord injury in a tree shrew model.",
    "The improvement in locomotor function is associated with CNTF-STAT3 signaling pathway activation.",
    "Tree shrews were used as an animal model that more closely resembles primates compared to rodents."
